strings:
<voice_0x01000ADD><se_high>Jessica: Ah, there you are!
So, what are you two up to?

<voice_0x01000ADE><se_low>Yangus: Up to?
Me an' the guv was just talkin', that's all.

<voice_0x01000ADF><se_high>Jessica: Guv, huh?
I've been meaning to ask you about that.
<voice_0x01000AE0><se_high>Jessica: You know, he doesn't exactly look like your governor. If anything, it looks the other way around. What's the story?
<voice_0x01000AE2><se_low>Yangus: The story of 'ow me an' the guv fell in together is an epic tale, full o' laughter, thrills, and tears...

<voice_0x01000AE3><se_high>Jessica: It is, is it?
Well, why don't you just give me the highlights?

<voice_0x01000AE4><se_low>Yangus: Awright, I will!
It all started on a fine, summer's day...
The sound of insects was deafenin'...

<voice_0x01000AE5><se_low>Yangus: I'd just decided to make a clean break of it.
I was well 'acked off wiv the old bandithood.
<voice_0x01000AE6><se_low>Yangus: So I decided to leave the town that I lived in me 'ole life and start fresh, like.
